<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/23005516">贾诩做了太尉，孙权为何「笑之」？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1383099" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">魏略曰：文帝得诩之对太祖，故即位首登上司。荀勖别传曰：晋司徒阙，武帝问其人於勖。答曰：“三公具瞻所归，不可用非其人。昔魏文帝用贾诩为三公，孙权笑之。”</div>


</div>
