<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="74">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-xiao-long-32-1" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-xiao-long-32-1" class="zg-link" title="张小龙">张小龙</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$seky-chyo" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/seky-chyo" class="zg-link" title="Seky Chyo">Seky Chyo</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$a13979103872" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/a13979103872" class="zg-link" title="王二">王二</a></span>
